title: Pick a website
body:
One member of the community has provided a website so far - Bobby: https://eurobob.github.io/ourshib/index.html

Should we go with this website for now?

Note: We will have to purchase a domain name and host this site there / have the domain point to the github.io page.
choices: Yes, this should be our website
No, let's wait for more options
